    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is my absolute pride and joy\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it\u2019s still in showroom condition! It drives like a dream and looks so flawless you\u2019d think it just rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
