      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips, scratches, or swirls, protected by climate-controlled storage and a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather bolsters show no wear, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a whisper-quiet engine and a comprehensive folder of meticulous dealership service records. With exceptionally low mileage and an undercarriage as clean as the bodywork, this is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to acquire a flawless example of this model.",
